
         ╔════════════════════════════════════════╗
         ║                openwaifu               ║
         ║       discord bot + local pi repo      ║
         ╚════════════════════════════════════════╝

  SETUP
    cp 01_BOT/.env.example 01_BOT/.env
    npm run setup

  RUN
    npm run dev

  VERIFY
    npm run check
    npm run test

  BOT
    01_BOT  … discord.js runtime, replies to all non-bot messages, keeps per-scope sessions, manages Discord via tools

  EXTENSIONS
    persona   … loads extension-local PERSONA file into pi system prompt
    scheduler … adds, updates, lists, and cancels one-time and cron-based Discord tasks that run in fresh clean pi sessions for current user/session

  SKILLS
    (none)

  LINKS
    pi-coding-agent  https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono
